data.description: INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY to own this THREE STORY ROWHOUSE built in 2006 with a TWO CAR GARAGE and loaded with upgrades in the booming VCU district! The first floor features all hardwood floors, huge living room with bay window, half bath, and EAT-IN kitchen with GRANITE COUNTERS, STAINLESS APPLIANCES, MAPLE CABINETS, and RECESSED LIGHTING. The second floor features two large bedrooms each with their own full bath and plenty of closet space.  Washer + dryer in the hallway.  Third floor features two more large bedrooms with a shared full bath and ample closet space.  Fenced rear patio, dual zone HVAC, and so much more.  1 Year Home Warranty Included.  Don't miss out and book your private showing today!
